Package: libmoosex-traitfor-meta-class-betteranonclassnames-perl
Version: 0.002003-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Debian Perl Group <pkg-perl-maintainers@lists.alioth.debian.org>
Installed-Size: 28
Depends: perl, libautobox-core-perl, libmoose-perl, libnamespace-autoclean-perl
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://metacpan.org/release/MooseX-TraitFor-Meta-Class-BetterAnonClassNames
Description: helper for MooseX::Util to generate anonymous class names
 MooseX::TraitFor::Meta::Class::BetterAnonClassNames helps MooseX::Util's
 with_traits() method to create better named anonymous classes.
 .
  my $anon_class_name = with_traits('Zombie::Catcher', 'SomeTrait');
 .
 now becomes
 .
  Zombie::Catcher::__ANON__::SERIAL::1
 .
 rather than
 .
  Moose::Meta::Class::__ANON__::SERIAL::1
